     F*  LER038 - Update of PF/LEOACTPD (Leo LC Actions) with         *
     F*           the details from Leo LCNEGS and LCLOG files         *
     F*                                                               *
     F*  Function:  This program was created for the Leo Midas        *
     F*             Integration project. The PF/LEOACTPD is used      *
     F*             by the Midas program LER035 to update the files   *
     F*             PF/HISACT and PF/FACACT. This program is called   *
     F*             by the Leo program CMIU35. CMIU35 takes the Leo   *
     F*             Actions from the LCNEGS,LCLOGD and LCLOGS files   *
     F*             and passes them to this program as a parameter    *
     F*             string. This program splits the string into the   *
     F*             fields and outputs them to the PF/LEOACTPD.       *
     F*             If an error occurs on the write, a return code    *
     F*             will be passed back to CMIU35.                    *
     F*                                                               *
